{"tid":1430940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"校長錢大康拒譴責警方 浸大學生會「罷 Reg」","createTime":"2019-08-08T01:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T16:27:59.000Z","uid":56881,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a14e97632e0e006991cb01dcfb653acffa8f5c73","tid":1430940,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:08:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%8C%A2%E5%A4%A7%E5%BA%B7%E6%8B%92%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83-%E7%BD%B7-reg-235300152.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%25BD%25B7-reg-235300152.html&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=aa028f4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E9%8C%A2%E5%A4%A7%E5%BA%B7%E6%8B%92%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E6%B5%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83-%E7%BD%B7-reg-235300152.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tWdTFXIYEGMUxroerFDskQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190808a080227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtWdTFXIYEGMUxroerFDskQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190808a080227.jpg&h=50981499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生會批評校方錢大康置方仲賢（小圖）安危不顧。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】警方前晚以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器為由，在深水埗拘捕購買十支雷射筆的浸會大學學生會會長方仲賢，並於警署附近拘捕另一名浸大學生。浸大校長錢大康應邀出席學生會昨晚舉行的集會，與300名學生對話，他拒絕學生邀請前往警察總部，亦拒絕譴責警方拘捕行，引發學生不滿。集會最終不歡而散，浸大學生會宣布今日「罷reg（停辦新生註冊日）」。<br />\n<br />\n學生會今日凌晨發表聲明，批評校長錢大康席間語言偽術，話語重重覆覆，磋跎歲月，苦無結果，又指校方在會長及學生被捕後，「方願出席最廉價的『對話』」，但校長不僅不願譴責警方濫權，更無實際承諾，形容是置會長的安危、將面對牢獄之災的風險不顧。<br />\n<br />\n學生會表示，對校方的做法深感失望，不可接受，宣布停辦今日的新生註冊日，以回應校方的失態。<br />\n<br />\nBU仔好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3fd3bbe34b7add6f61f7a28b848c0e19fc0b9f","tid":1430940,"uid":264992,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:12:15.000Z","msg":"BU呢期真係不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a45432ae09ebceef5f92b196324d4adc425428","tid":1430940,"uid":136115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54d836aef4c0ecf77c758c5029251caa6d35f953","tid":1430940,"uid":196924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:30:41.000Z","msg":"正式宣佈浸幼重新回歸大學行列, 復稱浸大<br />\n段崇智嗰間可以改稱支小"},{"pid":"2f20e1690469d585fef011e0cf47d31106be0327","tid":1430940,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小學雞"},{"pid":"d5d8c90c32763ac71c0e096c29b535c686e3be05","tid":1430940,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"要講得清楚啲 錢校長講一套做一套<br />\n又話要讉責 但又拒絕讉責"},{"pid":"5c8859708d398e587d0be72a1718571b7d0dcd68","tid":1430940,"uid":91271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d2447b99b06aea6f2d926ee9b65a2e705df5ce","tid":1430940,"uid":139461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edff3a18a3c2dd154ff4e44919df0bc446ecc139","tid":1430940,"uid":139461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}